# GPU Modular System Architecture

*[Architecture](../index.md)*

## Overview

VisionFlow's GPU modular system provides a unified CUDA kernel architecture for high-performance physics computation.

## Architecture

For complete GPU architecture details, see:

- [GPU Compute Integration](./gpu-compute.md) - Complete GPU implementation
